      "time": "~20s",
      "narrative": "Once the agents are working in production, the next question is simple. How do we make them better at the job, and how do we run them more efficiently as volume grows?",
      "demo_actions": "Open the post-deployment optimization area in Foundry or A365. Frame the goal as quality plus cost.",
