      },
      "time": "~30s",
      "narrative": "We start with quality. Foundry rubric evaluators let us score the agent on the work that actually matters in invoice assurance, using traces from real runs to shape what good looks like.",
      "demo_actions": "Open Foundry rubric evaluators. Show trace-based rubric generation or the evaluator setup flow.",
