        "screenshot": false,
        "visual": false,
        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~30s",
      "narrative": "Now we can run evaluations against those rubrics and see where the agent is strong and where it still needs work. That gives the team a repeatable way to improve quality instead of relying on anecdotal testing.",
      "demo_actions": "Run or review evaluation results. Show scores, failures, and examples.",
