      },
      "time": "~35s",
      "narrative": "With that feedback in place, Agent Optimizer can help improve the invoice-review agent. The important point is that we are tuning against the real job, so the agent gets better at making evidence-backed recommendations in the Waypoint context.",
      "demo_actions": "Open Foundry Agent Optimizer. Show optimization inputs, target rubrics, and an updated result or comparison.",
