        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~25s",
      "narrative": "Quality is only half the story. In production, cost matters too, especially if many invoice reviews are running every day across many suppliers and manufacturing programs.",
      "demo_actions": "Move to the A365 cost view or cost monitoring surface. Show model or run cost metrics.",
