        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~35s",
      "narrative": "This is where hill climbing comes in. We take what we learned from the stronger model and use it to move toward a smaller model that can carry more of the workload at a lower operating cost.",
      "demo_actions": "Show the hill-climbing setup or model comparison from larger model to smaller model.",
